text: Kenneth John "Ken" Williams (7 January 1918 – 29 November 1977) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Collingwood in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Profile at Collingwood Forever Category:1918 births Category:1977 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players Category:People from the City of Latrobe
